Valentin Fernandez Coria vs Jose Raul Capablanca
Exhibition Game (1914), Buenos Aires ARG, Aug-20 
Four Knights Game: Spanish. Symmetrical Variation (C49)

1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Nc3 Nf6 4. Bb5 Bb4 5. O-O O-O 6. d3 d6 7. Bg5 Bc3 8. bc3 Qe7 9. Nd2 h6 10. Bh4 Nd8 11. d4 Ne6 12. de5 de5 13. Bd3 Nf4 14. Nc4 Rd8 15. Bf6 Qf6 16. Qd2 Bh3 17. Ne3 Bg2 18. Nf5 Be4 19. Ng3 Nh3#
